"5 cups water","1 1/4 cups stone-ground yellow grits","3/4 cup (3 ounces) shredded sharp provolone cheese, divided","1 teaspoon salt, divided","  Cooking spray","1 1/2 teaspoons butter","3/4 cup chopped onion","2  garlic cloves, minced","4 cups thinly sliced portobello mushrooms (about 6 ounces)","3 cups thinly sliced shiitake mushroom caps (about 4 1/2 ounces)","1 teaspoon dried herbes de Provence","1/4 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper","1 cup chopped prosciutto (about 3 ounces)","1/3 cup dry white wine","3  large eggs, lightly beaten","2  large egg whites, lightly beaten","1 tablespoon minced fresh parsley"